<section id="oss">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Open Source</h2>
    <p class="section-intro">
      Terraform modules, ARG queries, and tooling that came out of real customer engagements.
    </p>
    <div class="repo-grid">

      <a class="repo-card" href="https://github.com/martinopedal/azure-analyzer" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <div class="repo-header">
          <span class="repo-lang powershell">PowerShell</span>
        </div>
        <h3>azure-analyzer</h3>
        <p>Automated Azure assessment bundling azqr, PSRule, AzGovViz and ALZ graph queries. Unified JSON + HTML reports.</p>
        <span class="repo-stars">⭐ 14</span>
      </a>

      <a class="repo-card" href="https://github.com/martinopedal/alz-graph-queries" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <div class="repo-header">
          <span class="repo-lang powershell">PowerShell</span>
        </div>
        <h3>alz-graph-queries</h3>
        <p>135 Azure Resource Graph queries for the ALZ checklist. Takes automated coverage from 49 to 135 items.</p>
        <span class="repo-stars">⭐ 7</span>
      </a>

      <a class="repo-card" href="https://github.com/martinopedal/terraform-azapi-aks-automatic" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <div class="repo-header">
          <span class="repo-lang terraform">HCL</span>
        </div>
        <h3>terraform-azapi-aks-automatic</h3>
        <p>AKS Automatic with ALZ Corp networking. BYO VNet, multiple ingress (AGC/NGINX/Istio) and egress options.</p>
        <span class="repo-stars">⭐ 1</span>
      </a>

      <a class="repo-card" href="https://github.com/martinopedal/linkedin-auto-poster" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
