          <span class="repo-lang python">Python</span>
        </div>
        <h3>linkedin-auto-poster</h3>
        <p>AI-powered LinkedIn post generator. Fetches RSS feeds, scores relevance, drafts in your voice, publishes via PR approval.</p>
        <span class="repo-stars">⭐ 5</span>
      </a>

      <a class="repo-card" href="https://github.com/martinopedal/ghec-vnet-runners-azure" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <div class="repo-header">
          <span class="repo-lang terraform">HCL</span>
        </div>
        <h3>ghec-vnet-runners-azure</h3>
        <p>GitHub-hosted runners with Azure VNet integration for GHE.com with EU data residency.</p>
        <span class="repo-stars">⭐ 1</span>
      </a>

      <a class="repo-card" href="https://github.com/martinopedal" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <div class="repo-header">
          <span class="repo-lang all">All repos →</span>
        </div>
        <h3>See everything on GitHub</h3>
        <p>Terraform modules, ARG queries, MCP servers, and CI/CD tooling from real customer engagements.</p>
